news.title: NoBroker raises $5 million in Series E round from Google
news.para: "Current funding will be used to expand and improve Nobrokerhood. Currently it operates in 15,000 societies in 11 cities. We want to reach to one lakh societies in the next two years," said Amit Agarwal, co-founder and CEO of Nobroker.

news.title: Sunteck Realty lease out two lakh sq ft to Upgrad in Mumbai
news.para: Upgrad will be paying starting rentals of close to Rs 300 per sq ft. per month on carpet area basis to Sunteck Realty. The total revenuegenerated from the project will amount close to Rs 2,000 crore over the entire lease tenure.

news.title: China: Country Garden's chairman steps down
news.para: The developer's Hong Kong-listed shares jumped over 7% in morning trading, compared to a 5% rise in the Hang Seng Mainland Properties Index

news.title: Vacate rickety Salt Lake flats in one month: West Bengal government to residents
news.para: There are 42 building blocks within Falguni Abasan, each block housing eight flats. The total number of flats adds up to 336. Eight flats in each of building Nos. B-5 and B-6 have been declared condemned by the authorities.

news.title: Migsun Group buys nine acre land in Delhi's Rohini colony for Rs 265 crore
news.para: Migsun Group has entered into a share purchase agreement with Yogi Raj Promoters, which owns this 9-acre land parcel, he added.

news.title: Telangana pays mere 0.1% of pending property tax owed to civic body
news.para: The RTI reply given to secretary of Forum for Good Governance (FGG) M Padmanabha Reddy reveals that 19 state government departments paid paltry sums between 2 lakh and 3 crore.

news.title: Mangaluru civic body agrees to review increase in property tax
news.para: A monthly general council meeting of the MCC held on Tuesday witnessed pandemonium when the Congress in the opposition did not accept the hike in property tax, which the urban local body implemented recently.

news.title: Pimpri Chinchwad civic body issues 5,000 property attachment notices for tax
news.para: The Pimpri Chinchwad Municipal Corporation (PCMC) has recovered Rs645 crore this fiscal, the highest recovery recorded for the tax department.

news.title: Action against Kanpur development body officials, staff in forged plots registry
news.para: Vice chairman, Arvind Singh in his letter dated february 23,2023 stated that charge sheet /suspension/ departmental action should be taken against them.

news.title: Ludhiana civic body seals two buildings over default in property tax payment
news.para: As per MC officials, both these buildings fall under commercial category and the owners had failed to submit the property tax, which amounts to around Rs 3 lakh.

news.title: How YEIDA went from Rs 642 crore loss in 2016 to record profit in just six years
news.para: Officials said that the Yamuna Expressway Industrial Development Authority (YEIDA) once reeled under huge debts and could not even pay salaries to its employees.

news.title: Aadhaar a must to sell or buy property in Andhra Pradesh
news.para: Registrations of sale deeds are being withheld at AP registrar's office without Aadhaar cards despite the Supreme Court ruling not to link it with essential services.

news.title: Ambuja Cements bags coal mine in Maharashtra
news.para: "Forward auctions for these mines have been started on 27.02.2023 and on the 2nd day of the e-auction, six coal mines were put up for auction," the coal ministry said in a statement.

news.title: Vadodara civic body collects over Rs 2 crore towards pending rent
news.para: Several elected functionaries, including mayor and Sayajigunj MLA Keyur Rokadia and assembly chief whip Balkrishna Shukla, have been meeting shopkeepers in the complex for the last couple of months over various issues, including overdue rents.

news.title: Income tax searches at Googee Properties
news.para: The company has been involved in several real estate transactions on hundreds of acres in south Hyderabad, officials said.
